subtitleNullable: Unifyied Rebrickable database with price and star ratings added informations
descriptionNullable:
This dataset has been created by merging two types of dataset: 
- [rebrickable dataset](https://rebrickable.com/downloads/) downloaded on 2023.11.14 
- informations about price, reviews and star rating for each set coming from [this](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/mterzolo/lego-sets) dataset

Preprocessing steps have been computer with Tableau Prep (the whole steps are represented in the image below), and involved cleaning, joining and aggregating data.
